\section2 RadioDelegate

A standard delegate with a radio button.

\table
\row
    \li \b{Type}
    \li{2, 1} RadioDelegate

\row
    \li{1, 7} \b{States}
    \li{2, 1} Hovered
\row
    \li{2, 1} ActiveFocus
\row
    \li{2, 1} VisualFocus
\row
    \li{2, 1} Pressed
\row
    \li{2, 1} Checked
\row
    \li{2, 1} Enabled
\row
    \li{2, 1} Highlighted

\row
    \li{1, 6} \b{Hints}
    \li \b with-icon
    \li Set whenever the delegate has an icon set.
\row
    \li \b hover-enabled
    \li Set when the delegate is supposed to show hover effects.
\row
    \li \b inside-list
    \li Set when the delegate is used inside a list view.
\row
    \li \b inside-table
    \li Set when the delegate is used inside a table view.
\row
    \li \b alternating-colors
    \li Set when the delegate should be using alternating row colors.
\row
    \li \b changed
    \li Set whenever the element should visualize a changed state.

\row
    \li{1, 1} \b{Attributes}
        \li \b display
    \li A hint indicating what sub-controls should be visible. \br
        Possible values:
        \list
            \li \b icon-only Only display the icon.
            \li \b text-only Only display the text.
            \li \b text-beside-icon Display both icon and text in a row.
            \li \b text-below-icon Display both icon and text with the text below the icon.
        \endlist


\endtable

\section3 Sub-Elements

\section4 Icon

The icon displayed by the button. Style it using the icon related
properties.




\section4 Text

The text displayed by the button. Style it using the text related
properties.




\section4 Indicator

A rectangle used to render the radio indicator. This should show a
radio indicator image if the delegate's state is checked.


\table
\row
    \li \b{Type}
    \li{2, 1} Indicator




\endtable




